These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-6-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, water
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: lily, tulip
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: satire, disaster
There are 2 different nationalities: italian, malaysian
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: march, december
2 different games are played: poker, monopoly
The people use 2 different means of transport: scooter, trike
1. the person who growstulip is not the person watching disaster movies##6
2. the person drinking water is on the far left##1
3. the italian is in an odd position##4
4. the person driving the scooter is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in december##5
5. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person playing poker##1
6. the person watching satire movies is the person who's birthday is in march##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |
| Beverage      | water   | hot-chocolate |
| Hobby         | tulip | lily       |
| Music-Genre   | satire | disaster       |
| Nationality   | italian | malaysian     |
| Pet           | march    | december         |
| Sport         | poker | monopoly        |
| Transport     | scooter | trike         |

